{"tid":2022144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教育界陣地戰（文革2.0降臨 光復教育界）","createTime":"2020-05-18T07:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T09:09:39.000Z","uid":350452,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"876dfb36949542b1483d2795d59090d91758cb88","tid":2022144,"uid":350452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T07:02:20.000Z","msg":"我係教育界教師，來緊開學之後形勢會好兇險，希望係度同大家分析同講解來緊我既部署，不定期更新我既情況<br />\n我既目標係學校上到位做野，盡量擋住學校既墮落，搶奪番學校既話語權同資源（之後會再慢慢講）<br />\n<br />\n中學界首先復課，中學老師要小心來緊會有好多動作，深黃通識老師或者歷史科都可能出事<br />\n<br />\n開學前準備功夫：潛龍勿用<br />\n我知大家都好憤慨而家香港既情況，亦都可能會有情緒想抒發，但現階段唔好現身表明立場，有既話都要del曬佢<br />\n<br />\n第一，如果俾老細知道你立場，佢一定唔敢升你做d重要post，驚你亂講野，校長最想就係平平安安沒事發生，如果太明顯你會有好多不滿政府同言論，都會令自己上位機會大減，記住，有權力先做到野<br />\n<br />\n第二，同事間既出賣之後來緊都會出現，可能為左搶你既位而出賣你，例如ig或者facebook，所以全部都要del曬佢，唔可以俾人cap到，而家要搵痛腳一定係言論出手，教育界大家都好著重自己份工同利益，所以千奇要小心<br />\n<br />\n所以，開學前要做好準備，人地都已經準備好開拖，教育界唔可以企係到捱打，一定要清好曬檯面同社交媒體，最好放份大公報係檯，作為掩飾，其他人都唔敢攪你。<br />\n來緊我都會番工開會準備復課既野，有咩野再同大家匯報同交代部署，你地情況係點都一齊係度討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9a32b756696d7c6863e3fddd370b1111248f3e","tid":2022144,"uid":350452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"P牌沒得推，希望有心人士幫手推post"},{"pid":"66b21085614365ad2967f46c5c1e86a6d6b1e998","tid":2022144,"uid":84505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"認真post，推"},{"pid":"35c6e0864cf9340d606ad87948524ff3158e3469","tid":2022144,"uid":350452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66b21085614365ad2967f46c5c1e86a6d6b1e998","tid":2022144,"uid":84505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"認真post，推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T07:09:21.000Z","msg":"感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6948ec20d8f6abf5b550e09926ba925f0b0d1916","tid":2022144,"uid":84505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"想睇點重奪"},{"pid":"74ac37ea789cd9c8b39bc92b0e9dafa378421f73","tid":2022144,"uid":52516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T20:01:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4775603d1c2d099d326a51fce4fe36e2fc90cbc7","tid":2022144,"uid":52516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T20:02:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6ec06f0814231b691d027a2c1d515e181d48138","tid":2022144,"uid":350452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4775603d1c2d099d326a51fce4fe36e2fc90cbc7","tid":2022144,"uid":52516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T20:02:03.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T20:02:28.000Z","msg":"感謝🙏🏻"},{"pid":"3bed6b360c651e5ba2f93e71a2865825511d043e","tid":2022144,"uid":350452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T20:03:35.000Z","msg":"會定期更新同發佈來緊公司既動作，有咩消息希望係度公佈！"},{"pid":"9c63de991ee575482016c9d5e33a29833afab56c","tid":2022144,"uid":198595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T20:29:37.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n得兩個讚搞笑？"},{"pid":"4819d32500fa4ac9990d9d0ff366570eb048cffa","tid":2022144,"uid":350452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c63de991ee575482016c9d5e33a29833afab56c","tid":2022144,"uid":198595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T20:29:37.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n得兩個讚搞笑？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T20:59:09.000Z","msg":"感謝🙏🏻"},{"pid":"f77154cd5da2222c8237c850e96a97c0222ec755","tid":2022144,"uid":198595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T21:28:03.000Z","msg":"推完再推 失眠屌那星"},{"pid":"b9104a3586e46e7058362b5f00b7c34793fe6134","tid":2022144,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T21:39:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4dde02eb32de371de769a76f4fa52308e3840bf4","tid":2022144,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T21:39:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0